Package: meedr
Title: Macroeconomic Expectations Data in R using the Central Bank of Brazil API
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Fernando",
           family = "da Silva",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "fernando@fortietwo.com",
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-7491-6930"))
Description: Provides quick and easy access to the data and statistics of market expectations regarding the economic indicators of the Focus report of the Central Bank of Brazil, through the Expectations System API. This data comes from several financial institutions, such as: banks, brokers, funds, consultancies, etc. This package offers an R interface to the API and other advantages, such as using a caching system and the option to use all the machine's cores (parallel computing).
